title: ELEMENT MAKE IT COUNT: UK 2015
description:
Congrats to Jiri "George" Bulin who won the MAKE IT COUNT contest in Manchester, UK!
George won a spot in the European Finals that will take place in Italy and a chance to win a trip to California to compete for Element sponsorship at Nyjah's park!
